name: Hatched Forms Bangon
description:
A study of creating a simulated plotted ink on paper look through an algorithm which generates hatched lines within custom polygons.

This is a special edition created for the Bangon event, a fundraiser for the benefit of the victims of typhoon Odette in the Philippines. Bangon is a Filipino word that means rising from a lying position or growing in strength, number, or importance.

2000 × 2000 GIF, 6 frames
Made in p5js
Created 8 Jan 22

Artist: @Yazid
